data.description: Lovely ranch located in a beautiful neighborhood. Conveniently located 5 minutes to shopping, and with in 15 minutes to Christopher Newport News University. You are also about 20 minutes to JBLE Fort Eustis & 15 minutes to JBLE Langley AFB. Large living room, A large family room with a gas fireplace. Eat-in kitchen, Primary bedroom with its own bath. This home also offers a screened in deck overlooking the large backyard. This home also has a whole house generator, HVAC and water heater within the last year.
